Happy Mother's Day Maa ❤️

Backstory:
So I stopped posting a year ago after Mother's Day this felt like the perfect time to start again🤭. Last Mother's Day we are on video call crying you mostly because of what I wrote for you me because amid all that chaos you were my only rock🥺. I may had a lot of friends but that surely was a tough time or you could say start of a very tough time and all I needed was a hug from you and this Mother's Day when you are just 2 seconds away from me I'm so insanely grateful😌. I don't need to tell you how much I love you you know I'm addicted to you😮‍💨 my day ends and begins with you everybody in this world comes second to me when it's about you❤️🫂 the thought that we are gonna be apart for a year already makes me cry 🥺🥺 so I'll stop my rant now🙂‍↕️ I love you so much and happy Mother's Day ❤️
